&gt;&gt; On 1/4/11 11:14 AM, Noah Levitt wrote:
&gt;&gt;&gt; Here&#39;s one way to crawl seeds only, and not even embedded images or anything, which seems to be what you want. Starting with the default order.xml...
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; 1. remove the scope rule acceptIfSurtPrefixed
&gt;&gt;&gt; 2. remove the scope rule acceptIfTranscluded
&gt;&gt;&gt; 3. add this scope rule right after rejectByDefault
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;newObject name=&quot;acceptIfSeed&quot; class=&quot;org.archive.crawler.deciderules.SeedAcceptDecideRule&quot;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;/newObject&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt; Hope this works for you.
